file.name: parameters-path.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.2"
paths:
  /info:
    get:
      operationId: info
      responses:
        "200":
          description: ok
  /info/{start_date}..{end_date}:
    parameters:
      - name: start_date
        in: path
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
          format: date
      - name: end_date
        in: path
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
          format: date
    get:
      operationId: info_date_range
      responses:
        "200":
          description: ok
  /info/{date}:
    parameters:
      - name: date
        in: path
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
          format: date
    get:
      operationId: info_date
      responses:
        "200":
          description: ok
